 src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過出到大陸，我真係唔敢亂過馬路<br />\n佢地d司機冇性"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T06:03:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  日日都過斑馬線 <br />\nD 紅Van 綠Van 的士狗 從不收油 <br />\n離遠見到踩油搏你停<br />\n<br />\n都試過係馬路 有紅綠燈 仲未轉紅 眨下眨下 <br />\n差唔多到安全島 一個司機直接踩油<br />\n好在我個下反應快 唔係我就瞓撚低左"},{"pid":"58a8e95dcd45cdb53607ff47a7648e7153b80660","tid":928771,"uid":21917,"like":72,"dislike":4,"score":68,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T06:03:57.000Z","msg":"深圳到今時今日 馬路都仲係廿年前咁 上星期返過去 明明紅燈同行人緣燈著咗 d車都係照過 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13271acef7770136deb01fe6fce651dedfab3e8f","tid":928771,"uid":85586,"like":95,"dislike":1,"score":94,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T06:05:13.000Z","msg":"明知大陸啲司機癲嘅都照學廢老揮個手就過<br />\n結果贏咗場交輸咗個女<br />\n抵晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7933b81db74b478f27e42e915032c842d9e960bd","tid":928771,"uid":62409,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T06:06:11.000Z","msg":"每次過斑馬線都係心理角力"},{"pid":"0274112aa6cf8fc5b7ada193299b62783abad23d","tid":928771,"uid":11719,"like":78,"dislike":0,"score":78,"quote":{"pid":"cbc8d34abadb910fd9d20007751777a267e343f2","tid":928771,"uid":90890,"like":14,"dislike":117,"score":-103,"quote":{"pid":"5ca677ed83c276949a0e44baca7e70d93ed2c0fc","tid":928771,"uid":193192,"like":668,"dislike":14,"score":654,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T05:53:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  其實香港D 司機都係一撚樣 斑馬線唔收油<br />\n只係香港人驚撚左D 司機 會停低讓"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T06:00:28.000Z","msg":"係香港，司機驚人咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過出到大陸，我真係唔敢亂過馬路<br />\n佢地d司機冇性"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T06:06:29.000Z","msg":"大陸司機心諗：好彩車死咗，車唔死手尾長"},{"pid":"c69ae9e36f195a2f6304d868e2f187dee5b01caa","tid":928771,"uid":170594,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"470d